Time flies by so fucking fast... Exactly a year ago I was about to start my adventure on the other side of the world. Even tho it was a rough time, I wouldn't want to miss it and I'm so glad to made the experience! There were up's and down's but that's life! I can say about myself that I grew a lot. And I'm so thankful to my host family and all the people I've met. You made these seven months to those which I won't forget. Ever. Just to those who don't recognize: It's freakin' New York guys! And I'm so in love with each part of it. There are so many spots I haven't seen yet, but I'm about to come back for sure. I really do miss the states and to those who love traveling as much as I do: never stop exploring the world!
